A great community allows its homeowners to feel a sense of privacy, security, and serenity, while providing a place to socialize, interact and celebrate life.
A great Club greets each member with a smile as if they are family, while paying close attention to their needs through personalized service.
A great home mirrors the homeowner’s personality, down to even the most intricate details that make us who we are.
Our Harbor Hills family values these ideals down to its core and it's evident in everything we do.
WHAT MAKES HARBOR HILLS GREAT
Building upon our industry leading Florida Home Building experience, our team of dedicated professionals have collectively built tens of thousands of New Florida Homes and now culminate in the homes that we build for you at Harbor Hills.
It's Our Life's Work and we are passionate about what we do.
Harbor Hills is family owned and operated and is backed by one of the nations's most prestigious institutions.  On any given day, family members and our extended Harbor Hills family are onsite and available to serve you.
IT IS WHO WE ARE
We invite you to explore our web site and learn about our one of a kind community.  Be sure to
subscribe to our YouTube Channel
and explore our
facebook page
.
We are especially proud of the tremendous impact that our Club has on our surrounding community and are pleased to report that in 2014 the club and affiliated organizations donated approximately $100,000 to various community charities.  Please take a look at our
community
service
page
for more information.
Of course there is no better way to experience Harbor Hills than to be our guest and visit us.  Call (352) 753-7000 or
email us
to inquire about our Get Away and Play program.
We look forward to seeing you at the Harbor Hills Country Club and sharing our Life's Work with you.
AN INVITATION TO YOU
Do you have questions or require assistance?
A team member is standing by to assist you.

MEMBERSHIP
Your Membership Awaits
Studies show, residents who are active participants in their community, and have strong social networks of neighbors and friends, live happier and healthier lives. Harbor Hills Members love to live the good life. Staying active and fit through golf, tennis, yoga, aerobics, swimming and social activities are just a few of the ways our members maintain their healthy and balanced lifestyle. For information on how you can start enjoying all the benefits of Club Membership, call
352-753-7000
.
Cheers to Health, Wealth and Good Living!
HARBOR HILLS COUNTRY CLUB MEMBERSHIP PRIVILEGES
Reserve tee times up to seven days in advance and take advantage of weekly golf outings exclusively for our members. Participate in clubs such as Harbor Hills’ MGA and LGA as well as the various golf tournaments, including Pro-Am’s with our Club Professional. Improve your game with private lessons from one of our Golf Professionals and compete at your highest skill level.
GOLFING ON YOUR TERMS
Reserve tennis court times up to seven days in advance. Get in shape with private or group tennis lessons from our seasoned tennis professional. Participate in clubs such as the Harbor Hills Tennis Association and compete locally & nationally in USTA recognized tournaments and competitions. Harbor Hills ten Har-Tru clay courts are lighted for evening play and meticulously maintained.
TENNIS
Our state of the art fitness center is fully equipped with Life Fitness exercise equipment. The equipment is balanced between maintaining cardio and aerobic fitness as well as toning and muscle strengthening.
FITNESS CENTER
The pool is heated for year round use. Swim laps, take advantage of one of our water aerobic classes or simply enjoy the amazing views of Lake Griffin from the pool terrace. Patio tables, chairs, umbrellas and lounge chairs are conveniently located alongside the pool deck & terrace; making this the perfect location for those leisurely summer days.
JR. OLYMPIC SWIMMING POOL
Private Jacuzzi, steam & sauna rooms are located in both our Men & Women’s Spa Facilities. Take advantage of our private changing rooms equipped with individual lockers, showers and bathroom facilities that make taking one of our many exercise classes or utilizing the fitness room a convenient part of your everyday schedule.
REJUVENATING SPA & SAUNA
Our Signature Grille is open seven days a week and serves dinner most every Wednesday & Friday as well as breakfast on Saturdays & Sundays. Our magnificent Harbor Terrace Dining Room serves a Piano Brunch every Sunday and special dinner & theater shows are scheduled throughout the month.
RESTAURANTS & FINE DINING
Do you have questions or require assistance?
A team member is standing by to assist you.
CONTACT US
HARBOR HILLS SALES
Harbor Hills Sales is conveniently located in the lobby of the Harbor Hills Country Club.  Our staff is available 7 days per week 364 days per year and is the only staff dedicated to exclusively selling New and Preowned homes in Harbor Hills for the past 25 years.  Our Harbor Hills Sales staff are experts in all things Harbor Hills.  We can answer all of your questions regarding club memberships, homeowners’ association, activities and events, new construction, insurance requirements, remodeling and much more; including all new incentives on new homes.
